st free cell on “parks and rec characters”.\n          - generic [ref=f1e749]:\n            - button \"Update TD Snap\" [ref=f1e750] [cursor=pointer]\n            - button \"Reconnect to TD Snap\" [ref=f1e752] [cursor=pointer]\n        - complementary \"Preview\" [ref=f1e753]:\n          - generic [ref=f1e754]:\n            - generic [ref=f1e755]:\n              - generic [ref=f1e756]: Preview\n              - paragraph [ref=f1e757]: Drag buttons to the exact cells you want, or focus one and use the arrow keys.\n            - generic [ref=f1e758]: Live · parks and recreation (tv show)\n          - generic [ref=f1e761]:\n            - generic [ref=f1e762]:\n              - strong [ref=f1e767]: Parks and Recreation Characters\n              - generic [ref=f1e768]: Layout preview\n            - generic \"Draggable preview of the new page's button grid\" [ref=f1e769]: Your words appear here in an original AAC-style layout. TD Snap may render symbols and spacing differently.\n          - generic [ref=f1e847]:\n            - paragraph [ref=f1e848]: Existing buttons are locked. Focus a new button and use the arrow keys for precise placement.\n            - generic \"Communicative function colors\" [ref=f1e849]:\n              - generic [ref=f1e850]: Question\n              - generic [ref=f1e851]: Comment\n              - generic [ref=f1e852]: Positive\n              - generic [ref=f1e853]: Negative\n              - generic [ref=f1e854]: Personal\n  - contentinfo [ref=f1e61]:\n    - paragraph [ref=f1e62]: Runs entirely on this computer · nothing is uploaded to the internet\n    - button \"Quit the app\" [ref=f1e63] [cursor=pointer]"}}
